questionsAndAnswers.question: How long will my project take?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: All project is different but assuming that there are no delays from your side of things a typical website will take between 2 and 3 weeks to be completed.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you help me with my logo and branding.
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. We offer a logo design service. This works much like our web design service where we will keep working on the design until you are 100% happy.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I already have hosting, a domain or email
Once the site is live how much does it cost to get things changed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You will be able to update the content on your website using our content management system. However, if you need something more involved or don’t have time then we will make any updates required for a charge. We also offer web maintenance for $150/per month which include SEO + Speed + Website
